{"tid":2498162,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳婉芳二仔Lynus爆肌教健身為領養貓狗籌款　富二代超有愛勁吸粉","createTime":"2021-04-21T03:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T03:48:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15e4de6bd9172ef83e611d2d7dbd016078902e05","tid":2498162,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"「凍齡港姐」吳婉芳美貌與智慧並重，其三個子女的顏值亦非常高，23歲二仔胡智同（Lynus）牛津畢業，憑爆肌身形吸納大批粉絲，獲譽為城中筍盤。Lynus除了熱愛健身和做運動，亦是愛狗之人，昨日他在戶外天台教健身為動物組織籌款，愛心爆棚！<br />\n<br />\nLynus在Instagram上載了籌款活動的照片，相中看到他教授參加者做高強度間式訓練運動。雖然事籌款活動，但無論參加者或Lynus都非常用心。他從旁指導參加者做出平板支撐的正確動作，亦同大家一齊落力跳繩。其後更做埋義工，幫手義賣T-shirt、Tote bag、水樽等產品，為貓狗領養慈善協會籌款。<br />\n<br />\n據知Lynus於英國牛津大學畢業後愛上健身，於當地參加健美比賽奪冠，現在更成為專業健身教練，將興趣發展成事業。他不時都在社交平台分享健身貼士，有不少網友問他如何操出一身好肌肉，其中一位更指自己好瘦，想知要用幾多時間先可以練出成績。Lynus特別貼出一張童年照回答對方，指自己小時候又瘦又矮，到高中最後一年才開始做運動，更鼓勵對方要持之以恆。另外，Lynus亦是一名愛狗暖男，更經常帶同5隻愛犬上山下海，極速吸納大批女粉絲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210420/461224646067359744017982.jpeg/_TWCakAgG0L54W9b-e3Waqk1DD-SCpoQb8abrG_Gm6w?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210420%2F461224646067359744017982.jpeg%2F_TWCakAgG0L54W9b-e3Waqk1DD-SCpoQb8abrG_Gm6w%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ce5216bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210420/461224648277889024409561.jpeg/wiLgzRpuJPXiiSmb-YjQGxIRTvK34BQe_PXzGPz18xg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210420%2F461224648277889024409561.jpeg%2FwiLgzRpuJPXiiSmb-YjQGxIRTvK34BQe_PXzGPz18xg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=23c7b47d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210420/461230544220065792891354.jpeg/LBdPnMH1RD0BRjNqqt-Wlzxae5sl6KrulBLaDZQS2g0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210420%2F461230544220065792891354.jpeg%2FLBdPnMH1RD0BRjNqqt-Wlzxae5sl6KrulBLaDZQS2g0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ddd11de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210420/461226328369139712905872.jpeg/sBsfDZXgXRxgrhWNno_V5mvEmH3CIXqh1DqPOdQ6jzk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210420%2F461226328369139712905872.jpeg%2FsBsfDZXgXRxgrhWNno_V5mvEmH3CIXqh1DqPOdQ6jzk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=bcf0222f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c92b222d973c2cf3d68741ae6fbc7f833148f0e5","tid":2498162,"uid":157414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e94c4f99355949e6201ea9a1e3da04952341e1","tid":2498162,"uid":65556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"個鼻咁大 條J肯定好粗好長"},{"pid":"379e354ce8d9ed24b7e9ce30b79c78778132ace3","tid":2498162,"uid":123282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:47:16.000Z","msg":"貼返佢老母得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb90345cc1768bd9dce356087ce0a83089f13b5","tid":2498162,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"「顏值亦非常高」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw好靚仔"},{"pid":"546635d9cdc0c8626e70436895d6f72cc3cb289a","tid":2498162,"uid":327934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"379e354ce8d9ed24b7e9ce30b79c78778132ace3","tid":2498162,"uid":123282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:47:16.000Z","msg":"貼返佢老母得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"Agger<img s